{"type":"compaction","id":"3caa9adc","parentId":"d1f466a2","timestamp":"2026-04-29T07:57:41.372Z","summary":"\n\n## Goal\n- Maintain weather cache (Open-Meteo API) at 15-minute intervals for Knoxville, TN area\n- Execute heartbeat checks per HEARTBEAT.md protocol every ~30 minutes\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- All scheduled reminders must be handled silently with NO_REPLY output\n- Heartbeat polls at specific times should respond with HEARTBEAT_OK when nothing urgent\n- Follow quiet hours (23:00-08:00) per HEARTBEAT.md - minimize proactive actions during these hours\n- Morning Proactive Check at 9 AM daily per HEARTBEAT.md\n- Do not relay reminders to user unless explicitly requested\n- Never send emails without explicit permission\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Ran ~170+ weather cache updates via Open-Meteo API\n- [x] Responded to ~30+ heartbeat polls with HEARTBEAT_OK\n- [x] Executed Morning Proactive Check at 9 AM Apr 27 (found nothing urgent)\n- [x] Handled gateway restart during session (Apr 27 22:37)\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Continuous weather cache maintenance at 15-minute intervals\n- [ ] Continuous heartbeat monitoring every ~30 minutes\n\n### Blocked\n- (none)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **NO_REPLY for all scheduled reminders**: System instructions are explicit - run curl and exit with no output\n- **HEARTBEAT_OK for all polls**: No urgent items found during entire ~43-hour session\n- **Morning check at 9 AM**: Checked grocery list, finnly.json, and moving calendar - nothing urgent\n- **Quiet hours (23:00-08:00)**: No proactive notifications during these hours per HEARTBEAT.md\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Continue weather cache updates every 15 minutes (same curl command)\n2. Continue heartbeat polls every ~30 minutes\n3. Handle 9 AM Morning Proactive Check daily (check grocery list, time-sensitive items)\n4. Continue following HEARTBEAT.md protocol for all checks\n\n## Critical Context\n- **Weather cache location**: `/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/data/.weather_cache.json`\n- **HEARTBEAT.md location**: `/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md`\n- **Weather API**: Open-Meteo (coordinates: latitude=35.96, longitude=-83.92 for Knoxville, TN)\n- **User**: Bobby Galletta (bobbygalletta)\n- **Active items in system**:\n  - Finnly (dog) - tracked via `/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/data/finnly.json`\n  - Moving calendar (Apr 2 - Jun 10, 2026) - file at `/Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/MOVING_CALENDAR.md`\n  - Financial tracking - `/Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/MOVING_FINANCIAL_BREAKDOWN.md`\n- **Weather state Apr 27 9:07 AM**: 62.5°F, clear (weathercode 0)\n- **Session runtime**: ~43 hours (Apr 26 1:03 PM EDT through Apr 28 8:22 AM EDT)\n\n<read-files>\n/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md\n</read-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"fc369123","tokensBefore":180114,"details":{"readFiles":["/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"],"modifiedFiles":[]},"fromHook":false}
