{"type":"message","id":"f569d50d","parentId":"30383f03","timestamp":"2026-05-01T12:47:50.268Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Grocery list found. Let me check if there are urgent items.\n","thinkingSignature":"3e1706df144f5053e3621e5ddf9a73cd411bdc79d463d8b4fd1e6dc9aefbf73e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c8myj5ren4at_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/Desktop/Research/SecondBrain/Skills/grocery-list/ 2>/dev/null; cat ~/Desktop/Research/SecondBrain/Skills/grocery-list/*.md 2>/dev/null | head -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":211,"output":85,"cacheRead":105920,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106216,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777639664930,"responseId":"0643d3f1dd3432d16f059f06c5b6b854"}}
{"type":"message","id":"96209219","parentId":"f569d50d","timestamp":"2026-05-01T12:47:50.381Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_c8myj5ren4at_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"SKILL.md\n# Grocery List Skill\n\nWhen Bobby says to add something to his \"grocery list\", \"list\", \"shopping list\", or similar — add it to the **Grocery** list in Reminders.\n\n## The Rule\n\n| Bobby says... | Action |\n|---------------|--------|\n| \"add [item] to grocery list\" | → Add to **Grocery** list |\n| \"add [item] to my list\" | → Add to **Grocery** list |\n| \"add [item] to shopping list\" | → Add to **Grocery** list |\n| \"remind me to buy [item]\" | → Add to **Reminders** list |\n| \"remind me to [anything else]\" | → Add to **Reminders** list |\n\n## Key Difference\n\n- **Grocery list** = items to buy (food, household)\n- **Reminders** = tasks, todos, appointments\n\n## Command Format\n\n```bash\n# For Grocery list\nremindctl add \"[item]\" --list \"Grocery\"\n\n# For Reminders (only when Bobby says \"remind me to\")\nremindctl add \"[reminder text]\" --list \"Reminders\"\n```\n\n## Examples"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":31,"aggregated":"SKILL.md\n# Grocery List Skill\n\nWhen Bobby says to add something to his \"grocery list\", \"list\", \"shopping list\", or similar — add it to the **Grocery** list in Reminders.\n\n## The Rule\n\n| Bobby says... | Action |\n|---------------|--------|\n| \"add [item] to grocery list\" | → Add to **Grocery** list |\n| \"add [item] to my list\" | → Add to **Grocery** list |\n| \"add [item] to shopping list\" | → Add to **Grocery** list |\n| \"remind me to buy [item]\" | → Add to **Reminders** list |\n| \"remind me to [anything else]\" | → Add to **Reminders** list |\n\n## Key Difference\n\n- **Grocery list** = items to buy (food, household)\n- **Reminders** = tasks, todos, appointments\n\n## Command Format\n\n```bash\n# For Grocery list\nremindctl add \"[item]\" --list \"Grocery\"\n\n# For Reminders (only when Bobby says \"remind me to\")\nremindctl add \"[reminder text]\" --list \"Reminders\"\n```\n\n## Examples","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777639670381}}
