{"type":"message","id":"9bf983b4","parentId":"7755dce9","timestamp":"2026-05-01T13:33:13.949Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"9AM Morning Proactive Check — run the checks silently per HEARTBEAT.md.","thinkingSignature":"a27edf7b255404a1bdf674070cb5305a777a5e2551eb5fcf01b65530ea3f151a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_iuzjkygf4qb8_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/Desktop/Research/SecondBrain/Skills/grocery-list/ 2>/dev/null; cat ~/Desktop/Research/SecondBrain/Skills/grocery-list/SKILL.md 2>/dev/null | head -30; cat ~/agent-mission-control/data/finnly.json 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \"import sys,json; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print('Latest:', d[-1] if d else 'empty')\" 2>/dev/null; find ~/Desktop -name \"*MOVING*\" -o -name \"*moving*\" 2>/dev/null | head -5"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":223,"output":171,"cacheRead":106496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106890,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777642384305,"responseId":"0643de91b6bc788685dd2451eafab75a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c760d50b","parentId":"9bf983b4","timestamp":"2026-05-01T13:33:15.879Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_iuzjkygf4qb8_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"SKILL.md\n# Grocery List Skill\n\nWhen Bobby says to add something to his \"grocery list\", \"list\", \"shopping list\", or similar — add it to the **Grocery** list in Reminders.\n\n## The Rule\n\n| Bobby says... | Action |\n|---------------|--------|\n| \"add [item] to grocery list\" | → Add to **Grocery** list |\n| \"add [item] to my list\" | → Add to **Grocery** list |\n| \"add [item] to shopping list\" | → Add to **Grocery** list |\n| \"remind me to buy [item]\" | → Add to **Reminders** list |\n| \"remind me to [anything else]\" | → Add to **Reminders** list |\n\n## Key Difference\n\n- **Grocery list** = items to buy (food, household)\n- **Reminders** = tasks, todos, appointments\n\n## Command Format\n\n```bash\n# For Grocery list\nremindctl add \"[item]\" --list \"Grocery\"\n\n# For Reminders (only when Bobby says \"remind me to\")\nremindctl add \"[reminder text]\" --list \"Reminders\"\n```\n\n## Examples\nLatest: {'date': 'Apr 23, 2026', 'waterAM': False, 'waterPM': False, 'breakfast': True, 'dinner': False, 'walk1': True, 'walk2': True, 'walk3': False, 'walk1Poop': True, 'walk2Poop': False, 'walk3Poop': False, 'treats': 2}\n/Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/Research/SecondBrain/AppIdeas/AppIdea1/node_modules/react-native-screens/android/src/main/java/com/swmansion/rnscreens/fragment/restoration/AutoRemovingFragment.kt\n/Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/Moving/MOVING_CALENDAR.md\n/Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/Moving/MOVING_FINANCIAL_BREAKDOWN.md"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1742,"aggregated":"SKILL.md\n# Grocery List Skill\n\nWhen Bobby says to add something to his \"grocery list\", \"list\", \"shopping list\", or similar — add it to the **Grocery** list in Reminders.\n\n## The Rule\n\n| Bobby says... | Action |\n|---------------|--------|\n| \"add [item] to grocery list\" | → Add to **Grocery** list |\n| \"add [item] to my list\" | → Add to **Grocery** list |\n| \"add [item] to shopping list\" | → Add to **Grocery** list |\n| \"remind me to buy [item]\" | → Add to **Reminders** list |\n| \"remind me to [anything else]\" | → Add to **Reminders** list |\n\n## Key Difference\n\n- **Grocery list** = items to buy (food, household)\n- **Reminders** = tasks, todos, appointments\n\n## Command Format\n\n```bash\n# For Grocery list\nremindctl add \"[item]\" --list \"Grocery\"\n\n# For Reminders (only when Bobby says \"remind me to\")\nremindctl add \"[reminder text]\" --list \"Reminders\"\n```\n\n## Examples\nLatest: {'date': 'Apr 23, 2026', 'waterAM': False, 'waterPM': False, 'breakfast': True, 'dinner': False, 'walk1': True, 'walk2': True, 'walk3': False, 'walk1Poop': True, 'walk2Poop': False, 'walk3Poop': False, 'treats': 2}\n/Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/Research/SecondBrain/AppIdeas/AppIdea1/node_modules/react-native-screens/android/src/main/java/com/swmansion/rnscreens/fragment/restoration/AutoRemovingFragment.kt\n/Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/Moving/MOVING_CALENDAR.md\n/Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/Moving/MOVING_FINANCIAL_BREAKDOWN.md","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777642395879}}
